    "It assists scholars in locating appropriate sources for literature reviews, filtering references based on relevance, date, citations, and discipline, and enables easy access to full-text publications.",
    "Its free resources, especially the Zotero plugin and browser extension, allow users to further ease the literature evaluation process.",
    "Literature MappingLiterature mapping software are instrumental in discovering scholarly articles by exploring connections between publications.",
    "They enable researchers to generate visual maps of the existing literature based on citations, authors, funders, keywords, and other metadata [9].",
